desc.en: Get ready to see the world's best gamers at the IEM Katowice in Starcraft 2 from the Spodek Arena. This is from day 1 of the group stage.

title.en: Heroes of the Storm: HGC EU Summer Regional 2016

desc.en: With the Heroes of the Storm Summer Regional right here you can relive the best of the best.

Eight teams from around the world gathered in Katowice, Poland in order to fight for their share of a minimum 100.000 dollars prize pool as well as the prestigious title and trophy, and none of them were willing to give up their chance without a fight. This game is between ESC Ever and Team SoloMid.

title.en: Heroes of the Storm: HGC NA Spring Regional 2016

desc.en: North America Spring Regional Championship took place at ESL Studio, Burbank in California. Top 2 will qualify for the 2016 Heroes of the Storm Spring Global Championship, and the winning team will skip the first group stage there. See the teams compete in NA Spring Regional Championship for the prize pool of 1.000.000 dollars. This game is the Grand Final between Team Naventic and Cloud9.

DOTA 2 ESL One is back this time from Hamburg. It is the eighth time and ESL's first ever event in the Barclaycard Arena of Hamburg. Only the best teams are ready to compete in the ESL One Hamburg, where the prestigious prize pool is $1,000,000 USD

2018 marks the fifth year in a row that Cologne will be greeting players, talents and fans for a whole weekend of pure Counter-Strike: Global Offensive action from July 6th to 8th at ESL One Cologne 2018! Forget everything you have seen before and get ready for awesome matches, fun fan activities around the event, signing sessions with the teams and much more!

16 of the world's best CS:GO teams will attend the group stage of ESL One Cologne 2018 but only the very best will make it to the LANXESS arena. Here we have crowned new legends, watched the underdog defeat the fan's favorite and witnessed the best teams fall only to rise again. Year after year ESL One Cologne has seen trophies lifted and tears being shed by players and fans alike.
